description:
Stellar Repair for Active Directory is a professional software that repairs corrupt Active Directory database files with all security features and permissions.

Stellar Repair for Active Directory is a professional software that repairs corrupt Active Directory database files with all security features and permissions. The software restores all AD objects to a new AD database having the same domain name on another machine.
- Repairs users, groups, computers, and their properties
- Recovers objects like InetOrgPerson, MsMq, Printer, Contacts
- Supports Windows Server 2019, 2016, 2012, 2008 and 2003
